      "content": "<h2>Warm-up (2-3 min)</h2>\n<p>Week 14 review:</p>\n<pre><code>language → ?\nword → ?\nChinese language (lujvo) → ?\n</code></pre>\n<p>(Answers: <code>bangu</code>, <code>valsi</code>, <code>junbau</code>)</p>\n"
