    {
      "type": "material",
      "content": "<h2>New Material (5-7 min)</h2>\n<h3>New Vocabulary</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Lojban</th>\n<th>Place Structure</th>\n<th>English</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><code>djedi</code></td>\n<td>x1 is a day of week/month x2</td>\n<td>day</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>jeftu</code></td>\n<td>x1 is a week of month/year x2</td>\n<td>week</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>masti</code></td>\n<td>x1 is a month of year x2</td>\n<td>month</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>nanca</code></td>\n<td>x1 is a year</td>\n<td>year</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>cacra</code></td>\n<td>x1 is an hour</td>\n<td>hour</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Using Time Words</h3>\n<pre><code>ti djedi\n</code></pre>\n<p>This is a day.</p>\n<pre><code>mi gunka pa jeftu\n</code></pre>\n<p>I work one week.</p>\n<pre><code>la .alis. cu xabju ti re nanca\n</code></pre>\n<p>Alice lives here two years.</p>\n<h3>With Numbers</h3>\n<pre><code>ci djedi\n</code></pre>\n<p>Three days.</p>\n<pre><code>re jeftu\n</code></pre>\n<p>Two weeks.</p>\n<pre><code>pa re masti\n</code></pre>\n<p>Twelve months.</p>\n<h3>Key Point</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>These words name time periods. Use numbers to quantify them.</p>\n</blockquote>\n",
      "title": "New Material (5-7 min)"
